582
01:12:35,650 --> 01:12:37,190
Ngồi nguyên.

583
01:12:58,350 --> 01:12:59,740
Sét kìa.

584
01:12:59,950 --> 01:13:01,930
Kế hoạch đấy.

585
01:13:36,800 --> 01:13:38,320
Chúng ta cần chỗ nấp.

586
01:13:38,820 --> 01:13:40,320
Kia.

